# [6LO](../wg/6lo.html)

## Summary

The 6LO Working Group (WG) met during IETF 126. The session covered working group document updates, leadership changes, and technical discussions on semantic addressing, Neighbor Discovery address assignment options, and Static Context Header Compression (SCHC) integrations across various link layers. 

An important leadership update was announced: Laurent Toutain will join Carles Gomez and Shwetha Bhandari as the third co-chair of the 6LO working group. 

Key drafts discussed included the Path-Aware Semantic Addressing (PASA) draft, the Generic Address Assignment Option (GAAO) draft, [draft-ietf-6lo-schc-15dot4](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-6lo-schc-15dot4/), [draft-ietf-6lo-owc](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-6lo-owc/), and [draft-ietf-6lo-rfc8163-bis](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-6lo-rfc8163-bis/).

