### 5. Transmission of IPv6 Packets over Short-Range OWC
* **Presenter:** Younghwan Choi
* **Slide Deck:** [Transmission of IPv6 Packets over Short-Range OWC](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-6lo-transmission-of-ipv6-packets-over-short-range-owc-00)
* **Draft Reference:** [draft-ietf-6lo-owc](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-6lo-owc/)
* **Discussion:**
  * Version 07 updates focus entirely on Section 5 (Internet connectivity scenarios). Figures 7 and 8 were updated to better represent the unique directional propagation characteristics of Optical Wireless Communication (OWC).
  * The concept of Optical Transmission Range (OTR) was introduced to clarify the connectivity boundaries.
  * Alexander Pelov noted that the document is concise and well-written but requested more working group reviews before scheduling WGLC.

